The '''medal of honor''' was a decoration consisting of a gold, ten-point medal emblazoned with a symbol and attached to a red, white, and blue ribbon. It was a high-class award offered to people deserving of recognition.

[[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] awarded [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] a medal of honor for destroying a [[Unidentified maverick moon|maverick moon]] on a collision course with the [[Unidentified planet (New Academy for Space Pilots)|planet]] housing the [[New Academy for Space Pilots]].

